##Fever. The doctor at the clinic has a fever

Micro Signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

The following article is from city and life, by Hou Weilin

Focus on people and lifestyles in the city. Such as the afternoon tea under the sun, years of static good, joy in the heart.

Often at two o'clock in the afternoon, the head nurse went out to tell the registered person that the doctor had not eaten lunch. A room full of patients immediately quiet down, for me to make a way out.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Wen | Hou Weilin

Before the Spring Festival, our fever clinic suddenly transferred a new suspected case of pneumonia. I put on a protective suit and went into the Laminar flow ward to collect first-hand data on the patient's vital signs and soothe his anxiety.

Over the next few days, the number of hospital visits continued to climb. At the end of the day, just yelling makes my throat go numb. Often at two o'clock in the afternoon, the head nurse went out to tell the registered person that the doctor had not eaten lunch. A room full of patients immediately quiet down, for me to make a way out. I think this is the "bridge" between doctors and patients. In a few short steps, it is paved with the most precious human heart. It was a very moving scene, tears rolling in the eyes. I bowed his head, quickly "bridge" to pick up a few mouthfuls of rice, and back to see a doctor for patients.

Came home from work one night, Hoarse and sore throat, completely unable to make a sound. Father said to take his temperature. When I saw 38.1 degrees Celsius, my heart skipped a beat. The mother put a mask on the whole family at once. I was sequestered in a cell at home. The next morning, she waved goodbye to her daughter and told her father to take her to her grandmother's house. Just did not expect, from the birth to the present did not leave the side of the daughter, this is a month. For a long time, video with her daughter is she and I are holding back tears, hang up after the dare to cry. Good thing his temperature came back the next day. To tell the truth, cough can not sleep, diarrhea appears when there will be psychological pressure. The support of my family and colleagues is my greatest motivation. Chest CT showed no pneumonia, and he recovered quickly and went back to work.

But my mother had a kidney attack last December and had to undergo five or six operations, major and minor, to remove the tubes. I can't believe it started right after the first surgery. When I was fighting on the front lines, the tubes in my mother's stomach and behind her were always killing her. Thanks to the Urology Department of Dr. Zhong, careful surgery, patient answer questions, let me remove the worry. When I got home from work in the evening, I wiped my mother's body, washed her hair, changed the medicine, and boiled the medicine for her who could not move during the operation

After the first-level response was initiated in Shanghai, our fever clinic became the front line of the "war epidemic" . Hospital leaders attach great importance to the hospital's brother departments have come to support us, to fever clinic to reduce some pressure, but also let us more quickly identify suspected new crown patients. With the establishment of the isolation ward, our procedures for suspected consultation and isolation have been further refined. A group of hospitals and a group of medical staff to support Wuhan, Support Public Health Center. Every parting is fierce, every word of take care is heart-wrenching. Still, I could see the light at the end of the tunnel. Hold on, hold on, let's hold on a little longer!
